Description:
    Creates a new Metalsmith + gulp.js + Swig project to publish on GitHub Pages.

Example:
    yo metalpages

    This will create:
      src/                  : Metalsmith source directory
      src/index.md          : index page
      src/metadata.json     : metadata to inject in templates
      assets/css/           : CSS files
      assets/css/index.css  : default CSS file
      assets/images/        : image files
      bower.json            : Bower manifest
      package.json          : npm manifest
      README.md             : Project's README
      templates/layout.html : default Swig layout
      templates/index.html  : index page Swig template
      build.js              : Metalsmith build process
      .editorconfig         : EditorConfig file
      .gitignore            : Git ignored files
      gulpfile.js           : gulp tasks
      Makefile              : project's tasks
